{"article_id":"LYnAmQMZaNOiMxKe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Houston Rockets General Manager Daryl Morey tried Sunday to defuse the rapidly growing fallout over his deleted tweet","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that showed support for Hong Kong anti-government protesters ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"saying","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"he did not intend to offend any of the team 's Chinese fans or sponsors .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"A short time after Morey posted that statement ,","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"the NBA said","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"it was `` regrettable '' that the deleted tweet offended many in China .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"That followed several companies in China ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"including some of the NBA 's major business partners there ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"lashing out over Morey 's original tweet .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Fostering strong relationships with China has been a priority of the NBA for at least three decades .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"The NBA has a China office ,","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"just announced plans","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"to add a gaming team in Shanghai to the NBA 2K League","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and officials in both countries say","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"as many as 500 million Chinese watched at least one NBA game last season .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Morey tweeted an image","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that read","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` Fight for Freedom .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Stand with Hong Kong . ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"referring to the four-month-old protests in the semi-autonomous Chinese territory .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"That led to Houston owner Tilman Fertitta turning to Twitter","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that Morey does not speak for the Rockets ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and sparking an outcry","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that included the Chinese Basketball Association","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"- whose president is Yao Ming , the former Rockets star center -","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"it was suspending its relationship with the team .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The Rockets ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"largely because of Yao ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"have an enormous Chinese following .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"But after Morey 's tweet , even the Chinese government 's consulate office in Houston issued a statement","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"it `` expressed strong dissatisfaction '' with the team .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"NBA Chief Communications Officer Mike Bass released the following statement :","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"`` We recognize","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that the views","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"expressed by Houston Rockets General Manager Daryl Morey","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"have offended so many of our friends and fans in China ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"which is regrettable .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"While Daryl has made it clear","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that his tweet does not represent the Rockets or the NBA ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"the values of the league support individuals ' educating themselves","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and sharing their views on matters important to them .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"We have great respect for the history and culture of China","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and hope","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that sports and the NBA can be used as a unifying force","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to bridge cultural divides","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and bring people together . \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Other criticism came from Tencent , a major media partner of the NBA in China with a streaming deal","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that is worth $ 1.5 billion over the next five years ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"and Chinese state television","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"both of which said","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"they would not be showing Rockets games .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"It was n't immediately clear","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"if Morey 's new tweets or the NBA 's statement","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that followed","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"would be enough","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to salvage those relationships .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":70,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":64,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":64,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":66,"right":68,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":4,"right":65,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":75,"right":119,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":10,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":11,"right":73,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":93,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":90,"right":92,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":87,"right":89,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":79,"right":86,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":20,"relation":"elabo